{"tid":986213,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE直播中收驚悚留言：要在1月30日殺死子瑜，我保證！","createTime":"2019-01-18T09:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T10:55:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"393979a75bed6646a61990b2505dc5721859d810","tid":986213,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"恐怖粉絲層出不窮，各國皆有，日前南韓女團TWICE進行直播，就有酸名直接點名時間、人名，放話要在那時候行兇「殺死子瑜」，粉絲看了大呼驚悚，已經反映給JYP娛樂經紀公司，希望能實際行動遏止黑粉。<br />\n<br />\n不過恐怖的來了，就在接近結尾的時候，一名帳號為「GFRIENDHATERS9」的用戶留言，直接寫下驚悚文字：「我要在2019年1月30日殺死你子瑜，我保證。（I KILL YOU TZUYU IN 30.01.2019. I PROMISE）」雖然TWICE本人好像沒有發現，但當時讓收看的粉絲都嚇了一跳，非常驚恐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3843/d3843629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3843%2Fd3843629.jpg&h=265bbefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE直播中收驚悚留言：要在1月30日殺死子瑜，我保證！（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\n恐怖留言的截圖立馬在TWICE粉絲群傳開，大量的轉發提醒與告知，零星出現「保護子瑜小隊 #TzuyuProtectionSquad」、「保護TWICE小隊 #TwiceProtectionSquad」、「保護子瑜 #ProtectTzuyu」等推文。目前粉絲已經回報給JYP娛樂，希望他們趕緊處理，提前保護藝人人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好得個講字啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe5b11b07ffa263eae1d16f0c5ed13dba3887c4","tid":986213,"uid":223790,"like":10,"dislike":27,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f450a349bb1845e082be0f67ebd4446a7759608","tid":986213,"uid":223790,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:18:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ac02b813d73b4b75304aa1dd860aa717f1e167a","tid":986213,"uid":176650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"快d"},{"pid":"6b7d5322c33f52d52d85b0b1600a52f4e777a062","tid":986213,"uid":223790,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f7e8545ca7bf947280353fd9eb93779f30a8d35","tid":986213,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"repl